{
  "texts": [
    "Our choice was based on predefining certain attributes of the required output.",
    "These attributes specify the type of relation being extracted, determining whether they pertain to a particular organism or a specific cell function.",
    "Incorporating these attributes makes the keyword selection process effective in focusing our search on finding literature directly related to specific aspects of the target network.",
    "We identified frequently used keywords in published papers related to genetic entity regulation and interaction.",
    "Fig 6 depicts the 20 most repeated keywords among papers used by RegulonDB for the manual extraction of the transcriptional relations of Escherichia coli."
  ]
}